## Recommendation letter

tha exoume 2 sections. ena gia akadimaika kai ena gia ergasias.
sto kathe item tha exoume

- fname
- lname
- email
- idrima / orgasnimos
- checkbox oti exei lavei consent gia apostoli email

ta emails fevgoun kai sto save as draft kai sto submit.
otan exei figei ena email to item tha exei status p tha fenete sto submitter. ta statuses einai:

- pending
- aporifthike
- elikse
- exei dwthei

## Formes

tha exoume sigoura 2 simeia pou kanoun show/hide alla pedia h ena section apo pedia.
to ena einai me to an eisai arren kai ti stratologia
kai to allo einai an eisai pantremenos me ta stoixia sizigou.
na doume ligo se UI pos tha to ftiaksoume. TODO

